{
  "stem": "15694.6",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was the given thing there, but quite a few-- I think the whole camp was present there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I estimated 10,000 and that is my estimate, but other-- some people said there were 20,000 in this camp.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Now on the sketch map, there are not enough barracks to house that 20,000.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It's, as I say, only a sketch map.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But as we are waiting as so, I was near the front, and I saw like some kind of a contraption like a football sort of a, a goal.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the-- only higher, not as wide, with two hooks on top.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And immediately, the idea shot through my brain, and I said, oh, two hangings.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And now, as I described it in the book, must I be ashamed that at this moment I've said two hangings, but thank god it isn't me.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So a short while we waited there, and in front of us a line of SS men with their rifles in hand.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I thought to myself, my god, if they-- where are the heroes of old?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now we are 10,000.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were about 100 in all.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Charge them.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "A few will be shot, but we, we just would overpower them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "If somebody would go and initiate this attack, I certainly would go with him, and perhaps the others would come because there would be no alternative but to be killed and we, we-- win or be killed.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But later, what happened a bit later, I didn't think at the time, but that was-- those were my thoughts.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyway, very shortly after that, the officers came along, amongst them, Goeth, which was probably the tallest man in the camp, except one prisoner, who was perhaps as tall and bigger as him.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Even the other SS men couldn't reach him.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
